---
title: Balsamic-Glazed Venison Steak & Parsnip Mash with Veggies & Sage Nuts with Choc-Chip Blondies for Dessert
description: The sticky, sweet tartness of our balsamic glaze really gets the mouth-watering. Drizzled over tender seared venison steak and a side of sauteed veggies topped with toasted sage nuts, this completely luxe dish will make the average dinner feel like a special occasion. For an added slice of heaven, dig into decadent choc-chip blondies for dessert!
